<p>I know I'm just a wee greenhorn here, but I had the same problem with this as Lumancer (Mostly his first three contentions). Granted I've only lurked the site for a couple years but this particular story kind of seems out of place in the Foundation universe despite the fact I feel the rest of the GoC case files fit pretty well. It just makes the Foundation seem unnecessary, and makes the antagonism between the Serpent's Hand/Wanderer's Library people and the GoC seem somewhat pointless with how tolerant and accepting the GoC seemingly is to the supernatural.</p>

