			<div class="content" id="post-content-2158010">
									

<p>My headcanon dictates that while the SCPF handles things that are difficult to understand and might loldestroy the world if let loose (or even messed with) the GOC is more like a paranormal police force that deals with the more 'everyday' paranormal stuff. Vampire or dragon? Ok to shoot/blow up. Endless stairs filled with a scary white face? That's the Foundation's job. I imagine that there is a lot of cross-pollination in missions between th two groups as they hand off stuff to the other. The GOC doesn't want another teleporting chair, but the Foundation doesn't have the resources to box up every last goblin they come across.</p>

